483    frac = (u0 - bp0[maxIndex[0U] - 1U]) / (bp0[maxIndex[0U]] - bp0[maxIndex[0U]



484      - 1U]);



485  }



486



487  fractions[0U] = frac;



488  bpIndices[0U] = iLeft;



489



490  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



491     Index Search method: 'binary'



492     Extrapolation method: 'Linear'



493     Use previous index: 'off'



494     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



495     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



496   */



497  if (u1 <= bp1[0U]) {



498    iLeft = 0U;



499    frac = (u1 - bp1[0U]) / (bp1[1U] - bp1[0U]);



500  } else if (u1 < bp1[maxIndex[1U]]) {



501    /* Binary Search */



502    bpIdx = maxIndex[1U] >> 1U;



503    iLeft = 0U;



504    iRght = maxIndex[1U];



505    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



506      if (u1 < bp1[bpIdx]) {



507        iRght = bpIdx;



508      } else {



509        iLeft = bpIdx;



510      }



511



512      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



513    }



514



515    frac = (u1 - bp1[iLeft]) / (bp1[iLeft + 1U] - bp1[iLeft]);



516  } else {



517    iLeft = maxIndex[1U] - 1U;



518    frac = (u1 - bp1[maxIndex[1U] - 1U]) / (bp1[maxIndex[1U]] - bp1[maxIndex[1U]



519      - 1U]);



520  }



521



522  /* Column-major Interpolation 2-D



523     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



524     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



525     Overflow mode: 'portable wrapping'



526   */



527  bpIdx = iLeft * stride + bpIndices[0U];



528  yL_0d0 = table[bpIdx];



529  yL_0d0 += (table[bpIdx + 1U] - yL_0d0) * fractions[0U];



530  bpIdx += stride;



531  yL_0d1 = table[bpIdx];



532  return (((table[bpIdx + 1U] - yL_0d1) * fractions[0U] + yL_0d1) - yL_0d0) *



533    frac + yL_0d0;



534}

750real_T rt_powd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



751{



752  real_T tmp;



753  real_T tmp_0;



754  real_T y;



755  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



756    y = (rtNaN);



757  } else {



758    tmp = fabs(u0);



759    tmp_0 = fabs(u1);



760    if (rtIsInf(u1)) {



761      if (tmp == 1.0) {



762        y = 1.0;



763      } else if (tmp > 1.0) {



764        if (u1 > 0.0) {



765          y = (rtInf);



766        } else {



767          y = 0.0;



768        }



769      } else if (u1 > 0.0) {



770        y = 0.0;



771      } else {



772        y = (rtInf);



773      }



774    } else if (tmp_0 == 0.0) {



775      y = 1.0;



776    } else if (tmp_0 == 1.0) {



777      if (u1 > 0.0) {



778        y = u0;



779      } else {



780        y = 1.0 / u0;



781      }



782    } else if (u1 == 2.0) {



783      y = u0 * u0;



784    } else if ((u1 == 0.5) && (u0 >= 0.0)) {



785      y = sqrt(u0);



786    } else if ((u0 < 0.0) && (u1 > floor(u1))) {



787      y = (rtNaN);



788    } else {



789      y = pow(u0, u1);



790    }



791  }



792



793  return y;



794}

1530



1531static void ap_LUf_boolean_Tint32_Treal32_T(real32_T outU[], real32_T outP[],



1532  int32_T N, boolean_T outS[])



1533{



1534  /* S-Function (sdsplu2): '<S211>/LU Factorization' */



1535  /* initialize status output */



1536  outS[0U] = false;



1537



1538  /* initialize row-pivot indices */



1539  app_B.k = 0;



1540  while (app_B.k < N) {



1541    outP[app_B.k] = (real32_T)(app_B.k + 1);



1542    app_B.k++;



1543  }



1544



1545  app_B.k = 0;



1546  while (app_B.k < N) {



1547    app_B.p = app_B.k;



1548



1549    /* Scan the lower triangular part of this column only. */



1550    /* Record row of largest value */



1551    app_B.idx1_tmp = app_B.k * N;



1552    app_B.mTmp1 = outU[app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.k];



1553    if (app_B.mTmp1 < 0.0F) {



1554      app_B.mTmp1 = -app_B.mTmp1;



1555    }



1556



1557    app_B.r = app_B.k + 1;



1558    while (app_B.r < N) {



1559      app_B.mTmp2 = outU[app_B.idx1_tmp + app_B.r];



1560      if (app_B.mTmp2 < 0.0F) {



1561        app_B.mTmp2 = -app_B.mTmp2;



1562      }



1563



1564      if (app_B.mTmp2 > app_B.mTmp1) {



1565        app_B.p = app_B.r;



1566        app_B.mTmp1 = app_B.mTmp2;



1567      }



1568



1569      app_B.r++;



1570    }



1571



1572    /* swap rows if required */



1573    if (app_B.p != app_B.k) {



1574      app_B.c = 0;



1575      while (app_B.c < N) {



1576        app_B.idx1 = app_B.c * N;



1577        app_B.r = app_B.idx1 + app_B.p;



1578        app_B.mTmp1 = outU[app_B.r];



1579        app_B.i_j = app_B.idx1 + app_B.k;



1580        outU[app_B.r] = outU[app_B.i_j];



1581        outU[app_B.i_j] = app_B.mTmp1;



1582        app_B.c++;



1583      }



1584



1585      /* swap pivot row indices */



1586      app_B.mTmp1 = outP[app_B.p];



1587      outP[app_B.p] = outP[app_B.k];



1588      outP[app_B.k] = app_B.mTmp1;



1589    }
